# Normalize line endings across platforms: store text as LF in the repo and check
# it out as LF everywhere. This stops Windows checkouts (with core.autocrlf) from
# showing the whole tree as modified. Binary files are auto-detected and left
# untouched, with a few common types pinned explicitly for safety.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.bin binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
